1. *Dešava* se da u ovo vreme godine sunce sve ređe sija. (It happens that at this time of year the sun shines less and less.)

2. *Dešavalo* je da odlazimo na more svake godine. (It used to happen that we went to the sea every year.)

3. Sve se *dešava* brzo u ovim danima. (Everything is happening fast these days.)

4. *Dešavalo* se da smo se igrali satima. (It used to happen that we would play for hours.)

5. Nismo se nadali da će se to *dešavati*. (We did not expect that to happen.)